```
SE16 → ZPPRT_EWM → Execute
Must have: ZZPORTDESC = 'MUNDRA' (or whatever your ZE11 text is)
```

**Check 3: Quotation has ZE11 text**
```
VA23 → Enter quotation number → Goto → Header → Texts
Check if ZE11 text exists
